<typeStatus box="[836,887,444,470]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[312,1247,484,510]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="11.[264,1324,284,510]" box="[312,1247,484,510]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis box="[312,455,484,509]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Distribution</emphasis>
. Known only from the Miocene amber of 
<collectingCountry box="[952,1126,484,510]" name="Dominican Republic" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">the Dominican</collectingCountry>
Republic.
</paragraph>
